<%- include("header") %>

    <section class="page-padding">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12">
                    <div class="page-title small-title mb-30 mt-4 text-center">
                        <h2 class="mb-1">Car Mate - Refund</h2>
                        <p class="text-black">Effective: June 06 2025</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="legal__content mt-5">
                        <div class="legal-text">
                            <h2>1. Cancellations by Clients</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    Within 24 Hours of Booking: If a client cancels within 24 hours of the booking
                                    request,you receive no payout, and the client gets a full refund (100%). No fees are applied
                                    to you.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Implementation: The system automatically cancels the booking and notifies you via
                                    SMS/email. No action required from you.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    More Than 24 Hours Before Session: If cancelled more than 24 hours before the
                                    scheduled session, you receive a cancellation fee of 25% of the service rate (e.g.,
                                    $25/hr rate = $6.25 fee). The client receives a partial refund (75%).
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Implementation: Fee is credited to your account on the next payout cycle
                                    (weekly/biweekly). Track in your dashboard under "Payouts
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Less Than 24 Hours Before Session: If cancelled less than 24 hours before, you
                                    receive the full payout (100%), and the client gets no refund.
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="legal-text mt-5">
                            <h2>2. Cancellations by Caregivers</h2>
                            <p>
                                With Notice (More Than 48 Hours Before Session): If you cancel with at least 48 hours
                                notice, no payout is issued, and the client gets a full refund (100%). You may incur a
                                $5 administrative fee deducted from future payouts.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="legal-text mt-5">
                            <h2>3. Disputes and Refunds</h2>
                            <p>
                                If a client disputes a completed session (e.g., via "Decline" after your completion
                                mark), payment is held in escrow until resolution. You’ll be notified via app push/SMS
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include("footer") %>